  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `rpcdaemon at devel branch (8850f3a)`\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Linux/OSX\r\n\r\nCommit hash: 8850f3a\r\n\r\nErigon Command (with flags/config): rpcdaemon\r\n\r\nConcensus Layer: prysm\r\n\r\n\r\nChain/Network: ethereum\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\ncall\r\n```\r\ncurl http://<IP>:<PORT> \\\r\n-X POST \\\r\n-H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\r\n--data '{\"method\":\"debug_traceBlockByNumber\",\"params\":[\"0x116E138\", {\"tracer\": \"callTracer\", \"tracerConfig\": {\"withlog\": true}}], \"id\":1,\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\"}'\r\n```\r\nand return a trace of block\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nrpcdaemon crashed\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\nrun rpcdaemon of code release v2.50.2, run test\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\n````\r\nEROR[10-05|07:24:30.929] RPC method debug_traceBlockByNumber crashed: runtime error: invalid memory address or nil pointer dereference\r\n[service.go:219 panic.go:884 panic.go:260 signal_unix.go:841 arc.go:67 bor.go:152 bor.go:465 evm.go:39 tracing.go:60 tracing.go:97 tracing.go:32 value.go:586 value.go:370 service.go:224 handler.go:511 handler.go:444 handler.go:392 handler.go:223 handler.go:316 asm_amd64.s:1598]\r\n````\r\n",
